cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper deals with deep learning algorithms for visual recognition tasks, specifically in the context of few-shot learning. The paper also incorporates multimodal information, which suggests that it could fall under the categories of computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and multimedia (cs.MM). Among these categories, cs.CV and cs.LG are the most likely as they directly relate to the paper's focus on visual recognition and deep learning.
